{"tid":1785593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【運動轉型】唸到點收運動燃燒落去到9月選舉","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T13:56:59.000Z","uid":105298,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"beed2fe5ac3ba909a549cf1186bcbd36c2b3dcbd","tid":1785593,"uid":105298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"依家既社會氣氛，好易將好多話題化大去講<br />\n由細既每日150，沙中線發展，東大嶼都會發展，<br />\n公屋編配制度，73公屋私樓比例制度，綜援制度問題<br />\n大到悔辱公職人員條例，23條，真雙普選等等<br />\n希望連登仔唔再沉迷係修例成功到<br />\n要令到香港人知道以上每一件事都關佢地事<br />\n將每一個議題化到修例咁玩<br />\n唸下點解修例由三四萬人發展到200萬人<br />\n唔搵d新關注，會比藍絲話為反而反<br />\n我地依家係要轉型，等所有香港人都關心我地自己屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c8987742ed5db0df4e3c48f0410af1a4987a25","tid":1785593,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f687b80be5a2f0162d7f35a68c3eb6851ee478b0","tid":1785593,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"3b915e2d130ef300e376654ed59135e864978cf7","tid":1785593,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c93c6cc2f143698a8a74a85bd2680307056a9965","tid":1785593,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"其實真係好撚多議題想強推落嚟比香港人硬食<br />\n呢個政府真係癡撚咗線"},{"pid":"3e7b7c4901bbe59445f7f86b2bc8a8c527602673","tid":1785593,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a700f7e52cd4606b1772e430d9cfe6c728b37e","tid":1785593,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.g